OL,5, The typical annual energy bill will    
OL,6, fall to #1,690 from April to the lowest
OL,7, for two years under the new price cap  
OL,8, set by the regulator.                  
OL,10,FIt means a drop of #238 a year, or     
OL,11,Faround #20 a month, for a household    
OL,12,Fusing a typical amount of energy.      
OL,14,FLower wholesale prices paid by         
OL,15,Fsuppliers have led to the cut in the   
OL,16,Fprice cap for April to June, which will
OL,17,Fbring some relief to billpayers.       
OL,19,FBut campaigners said bills are still   
OL,20,Fhigh and many will struggle to pay.    
